<h1 itemprop="name" class="title"><em>SMALL: Life and Death on the Front Lines of Pediatric Surgery</em></h1>
<p>Literate, moving, and illuminating, SMALL is a first of its kind look inside the world of a pediatric surgeon.</p>
<p><em>SMALL</em> won the <a href="http://www.writersleague.org/2014BookAwardWinnersFinalists?x=ITZsXl0yRfWdQDg0FS3RYW9pbkNgTpUc">Writer's League of Texas 2015 Nonfiction Discovery Award</a> and is a <a href="http://www.pen.org/blog/longlists-announced-2015-pen-literary-awards">PEN American/E.O. Wilson Literary Science Award Nominee</a>. Read an <a href="files/small_excerpt.pdf">excerpt from the first chapter of <em>SMALL</em></a>.
</p>
<p><em>SMALL</em> is available at <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Small-Death-Front-Pediatric-Surgery/dp/1611684420" title="Buy SMALL on Amazon" target="_blank">Amazon</a>, <a href="http://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/small-catherine-musemeche-md/1119314613?ean=9781611684421" title="Buy SMALL on Barnes &amp; Noble" target="_blank">Barnes &amp; Noble</a> or <a href="http://www.indiebound.org/book/9781611684421" title="Buy SMALL on IndieBound" target="_blank">IndieBound</a>.</p>
</section>

